Author: ready2rope
Text: Lmao I keep thinking about outfits I wore months or even years ago when I was slightly heavier or whatever and just, like, *cringe* thinking about how hot I thought I was, there are a few that stand out in my mind thinking I went out looking like that thinking I was hot shit, when in reality I know I must’ve looked disgusting and awful. It’s not like I even have pictures of myself then or anything I just *know* I looked like shit and it’s really upsetting knowing how differently I felt at the time.
